long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Do you like puzzle games? If your reply is yes you will love Electrio which is this fun game where you can control electricity.

Link the positive and negative electrons to build a circuit. You have to attach them so that they alternate positive, negative, positive, negative.. but be careful. You will need to organize your actions carefully because you can not cross paths.

To swipe Install this extension to play the Electrio game or offline with no additional downloads and no ads. 

You can contact us at support@724fun.com and share your thoughts and problems

After clicking the add the game to chrome button, you can find the game in the extensions section. If you wish, you can visit 724fun.com. If you wish, you can play again and if you want to remove it, you can remove it from the extensions section.
